ot participate the \u0130stanbul Shield Organization either.<ref>Tekil, S\u00fcleyman. ''D\u00fcnden bug\u00fcne Galatasaray, 1983, page 139.''. Arsel Matbaac\u0131l\u0131k Kol. \u015eti.</ref>\n\n==Friendly Matches==\n\n''Kick-off listed in local time ([[Eastern European Summer Time|EEST]])''\n{{footballbox  \n|date=September 18, 1931\n|time=\n|team1=[[Galatasaray S.K. (football team)|Galatasaray SK]]  \n|score=4 &ndash; 3\n|report=http://www.macanilari.com/getir.php?fid=193019314665\n|team2=[[Be\u015fikta\u015f JK]]\n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Taksim Stadium]], [[Istanbul]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=Unknown }}\n----\n{{footballbox  \n|date=October 6, 1931\n|time=\n|team1=[[Be\u015fikta\u015f JK]]  \n|score=0 &ndash; 0\n|report=[Report]\n|team2=[[Galatasaray S.K. (football team)|Galatasaray SK]]\n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Taksim Stadium]], [[Istanbul]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=Unknown }}\n----\n\n===Kaideli Heykel===\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|round=FB Stadium opening match - ''Kaideli Heykel'' match\n|date= 13 May 1932\n|time= 17:00\n|team1= [[Fenerbah\u00e7e SK]]  \n|score=1&ndash;2\n|report=[https://www.macanilari.com/getir.php?fid=193219334673] \n|team2= [[Galatasaray S.K. (football team)|Galatasaray SK]]\n|goals1= [[Alaattin Baydar]] {{goal|50}}\n|goals2=[[Mehmet Leblebi]] {{goal|25}}<br>[[Rebii Erkal]] {{goal|50}}\n|location= [[\u0130stanbul]]\n|stadium= [[\u015e\u00fckr\u00fc Saraco\u011flu Stadium|Fenerbah\u00e7e Stadium]]\n|attendance=\n|referee= Edward Allen\n|result=W\n|motm=\n|stack=yes\n}}\n\n===National Olympic Committee Cup===\n\n{{footballbox  \n|date  =May 27, 1932\n|time  =\n|team1 =[[Galatasaray S.K. (football team)|Galatasaray SK]]  \n|score =0 &ndash; 1\n|report=[https://www.macanilari.com/getir.php?fid=193219334674]\n|team2 =[[Fenerbah\u00e7e SK]]\n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Taksim Stadium]], [[Istanbul]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=Unknown }}\n\n==References==\n* Futbol vol.2. ''Galatasaray''. ''Page: 562, 595''. Terc\u00fcman Spor An